### Agentic Data Pipeline - Chat API
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000
### Non-streaming chat endpoint for multi-agent RAG queries

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Basic Query - Factual
# Simple fact-based question
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is machine learning?"
}

### Basic Query - Analytical
# Question requiring explanation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Explain how neural networks learn from data"
}

### Basic Query - Comparative
# Question comparing multiple concepts
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Compare supervised and unsupervised learning"
}

### Query with Conversation ID
# Multi-turn conversation support
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What are the main types of machine learning?",
  "conversationId": "session-001"
}

### Follow-up Query (same conversation)
# Continue the conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Can you give me examples of each type?",
  "conversationId": "session-001"
}

### Business Query - Revenue Analysis
# Example analytical query
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is the revenue growth rate for Q4?"
}

### Business Query - Trend Analysis
# Example multi-hop query
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Compare Q3 and Q4 revenue performance and explain the differences"
}

### Error Case - Missing Query
# Should return 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Error Case - Empty Query
# Should return 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": ""
}

